---
title: Spiced Beef & Parmesan Meatballs with Cucumber Salad & Herby Mayo
description: We’ve put a spin on beef meatballs with the addition of leafy greens and Parmesan cheese for this flavour-packed dish! These
meatballs speak for themselves - a simple cucumber salad and a drizzle of herby mayo are all they need to make up the perfect bite.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
